tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE project_documents (
    document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    document_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    document_path VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    access_level ENUM('read', 'write') DEFAULT 'read',
    member_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (member_id) REFERENCES team_members(member_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Documents (
    document_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    document_name VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    project_id INT,
    author_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES Projects(project_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (author_id) REFERENCES TeamMembers(member_id)
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  from_member_id INT NOT NULL,
  to_member_id INT NOT NULL,
  document_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (from_member_id) REFERENCES team_members(member_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (to_member_id) REFERENCES team_members(member_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (document_id) REFERENCES documents(document_id)
);
